Package edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.model

Class Event.Builder

java.lang.Object
edu.umn.nlpie.mtap.model.Event.Builder
Enclosing class:
Event
public static class Event.Builder extends Object
A builder for events, whether they are local objects, or distributed objects shared via an events service.

The getClientPool() property controls whether the object will be local or distributed. If it is not set / null, the object will be local, if it is set, the object will be shared with the events service.
